  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs zehlahs Nih-\ntâ agri/ un nehme to Akmini/\nkas tam bij Pagalwê bijis/ un\nuszehle to par weenu Sihmi/ un\nuslehje tam Etji wirfu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nosauze tahs Weetas\nWahrdu Betele/ bet papreekſch\nbija tam Pilsfahtam Lus Wahr-\ndâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs apfohſtida-\nmees apfohljahs/ un fazzija: Ja\nDeews ar mannim buhs/ un\nmann pasargahs us fcho Zetku/\nko es staigaju/ un dohs man\nMaist ehſt/ un Drehbes ap-\ngehrbtees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un liſs mann ar Meeru\npahreet/manna Tehwa Namnâ/\ntad buhs tam KUNGAM man\nce par Deewu buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un schim Akminain/ ko es\npar weenu Sihmi efinu uszehlis/\nbuhs par weenu Deewa-Nammu\ntapt/ un wiſſu/ ko tu man doh-\nſt/ no ta dohſchu es tew to def-\nmitu Teefu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXIX. Vodalla.\nJehkabs faſtohy Raële ar tahm Awim : 6.\nDsrdina Lahbana Awis/ un skuypsta Ra-\nëli/ fazzidams jewi eſſam Rebekkas Dehlu: 11.\nRalpo Raëles pehz ſeptin Saddus: 16. Bet\nLea toſp winnam Raëles Weeta peewesta: 23.\nPar to barrahs wiſſch ar jawu Tehwotsi Lah-\nbanu: 25. Tas dohd winnam Raëli arri-\ndsan: 28. Ruhbens/ Gihmeans/ Lewis/\nJuhba/ peedsemm no Leas: 31.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N Jehkabs mettahs\nUkahjop/ un gahje us to\nVaſchnu Seimini/ kas\nprett Rihteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſkattijahs/ un redſi/ tur\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "bija Akka wirs Lauka: Un rau-\ngi/ tur btja trihs Awju-Pulki\npee tahs paſchas/ jo no tahs Ak-\nkas tappe tahs Awis dsirditas/\nun weens leels Akmins bija wirs\ntahs Akkas Zauruma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur patt tappe wiſſi\nAwju-Pulki fads ihti/ nn tee no-\nwehle to Akmini no tahs Akkas\nZauruma/ un dsirdija tahs Awis/\nun likke atkak to Akmini us tahs\nAkcas Zaurumu jawâ Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jehkabs us\nteem: Manni Brahti/ no kur-\nrenes juhs effat? un tee fazzija/\nmehs effam no Ahranas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch fazzija us teem:\nPasihstat juhs Lahbann Naöra\nDehlu? un tee fazzija: mehs to\ngan pasihftam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiſſch uhs\nteem: Arrig tann labbi klahjahs?\nun tee atbilduja; gann labbi/ un\nredſ/ Raële winna Meita/ te nahf\nar Awim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch fazzija: Redsta\nSaule irr wehl augsta/ wehl La-\nka nevaid Lohpus pahrdſiht/\ndsrdijeet tahs Awis/ un eita/ un\npagannijeet tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee: Mehs ne\nwarraim/ pirns wiſſi Awju-Pul-\nki fads ihti tohp/ ka tee to Akini-\nni no Akkas Zauruma nowell/ fo\nmehs tahs Awis dsirdijam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad wiſſch wehl ar tee-\nrunnaja/ tad nahze Raële/ a-\ntahm Awim/ kas wiſſas Teh-\nwam peederreja/ jo winna gan\nnija tahs.\n"
    }
  ],
